::Shredder::

Shredder shakes his head, folding his arms across his chest. There was no way 
he was going to link himself to anyone he wasn't already linked to, it would 
get in his way. He might leave later and being dependant on Magmatron was not 
good in case that happened.

"I'll join you, but I'll skip the procedure. If you don't mind, I like to 
keep my root," he says, "I might change later when it is obvious we have won."
